result.name: Mr & Mrs Fox

reviews.text:
Amazing ambience.... awesome staff at Bar... Brian is an amazing mixologist... You should try his creations.... I bet if you can stop at one.

Fun place to be.

What was supposed to be one of those “work lunch spots picked out of convenience and don’t expect anything amazing” places turned out to be a great pleasant surprise ! 

We had the Hokkaido scallops for appetisers and I had the risotto as a main. Few weeks later I’m still thinking about the scallops which was one of the best thing I had that hk trip. It was fat, juicy and pure decadence.
Food was really good. Starter was crab and it was delicious. I had the fish and husband had meat for main and both were excellent. Desert we had an amazing petit gateau.

Great all round venue for drinks and food. Limited menu in the dining room but all meals offered are very well executed. Staff are friendly and attentive and strike the right balance of service. Highly recommend it for a post work, are dinner drink venue if you are in the area.
old styleish environment,nice food and wine. but a little bit expensive .fair service
